data.description: Experience the pinnacle of comfortable living in this immaculately maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, located at the end of a charming row and boasting a delightful surprise: a sparkling pool and hot tub. This exceptional property offers not only the coveted features of a finished basement, a large backyard, and beautiful curb appeal but also the added luxury of a private pool and hot tub oasis. Perfect for both relaxation and entertaining, this home harmoniously blends indoor and outdoor living, providing a tranquil retreat where you can unwind in style. Whether you're lounging by the pool, enjoying the spacious interior, or appreciating the privacy of an end-unit, this residence embodies the essence of modern, idyllic living and a 1 year home warranty included.
